        "details": {
            "description": "<p>A demonic presence animates the ship carrying demon pirates.</p>",
            "disable": "<p>@Check[religion|dc:23] (trained) to ward against demonic presence, @Check[arcana|dc:23] (trained) or @Check[occultism|dc:23] (trained) to weaken the demonic possession, @Check[intimidation|dc:23] (trained) to scare it away, or @Check[sailing-lore|dc:21] (trained) to confuse it; two total successes are required to disable the hazard.</p>",
